\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 1. Project Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 A fully functional OTT (Over-The-Top) streaming platform where users can browse, watch, and review movies and series. The system manages user subscriptions, payment transactions, multi-device support, and a rich content catalogue organized by genres \'97 all backed by a normalized relational SQL database derived from the provided ER diagram.\
