\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Implement all entities, relationships, and constraints defined in the ER diagram as a normalized SQL schema.\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Build CRUD-capable backend REST APIs for every core entity.\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Develop a frontend UI covering user-facing features (browsing, watching, reviewing, subscription management).\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Demonstrate advanced SQL concepts: weak entities, ISA inheritance, aggregation, derived attributes, multivalued attributes, composite attributes, and M:N relationships.\
